        <body>
            <div>
                <head>“To A Brown Boy”</head>
                
                
                <lg>
                <lg type="quatrain">
                    <l enjamb="no">That <rs theme="race">brown</rs> <rs theme="child">girl’s</rs> swagger gives a <rs type="rhyme">twitch</rs></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">To beauty like a <rs type="rhyme">queen</rs>;</l>
                    <l enjamb="no">Lad, never dam your <rs theme="body">body’s</rs> <rs type="rhyme">itch</rs></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">When <rs theme="love">loveliness</rs> is <rs type="rhyme">seen</rs>.</l>
                </lg>
                </lg>
                
                
                <lg>
                <lg type="quatrain">
                    <l enjamb="no">For there is ample room for <rs type="rhyme">bliss</rs></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">In pride in clean, <rs theme="race">brown</rs> <rs type="rhyme"><rs theme="body">limbs</rs></rs>,</l>
                    <l enjamb="no">And <rs type="personification"><rs theme="body">lips</rs> know</rs> better how to <rs type="rhyme">kiss</rs></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">Than how to raise <rs theme="race">white</rs><rs type="rhyme"><rs theme="religion">hymns</rs></rs>.</l>
                </lg>
                </lg>
                
                
                <lg>
                <lg type="quatrain">
                    <l enjamb="no">And when your <rs theme="body">body’s</rs> death gives <rs type="rhyme">birth</rs></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">To soil for spring to <rs type="rhyme">crown</rs>,</l>
                    <l enjamb="no"><rs theme="male">Men</rs> will not ask if that rare <rs type="rhyme">earth</rs></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">Was <rs theme="race">white</rs> flesh once, or <rs type="rhyme"><rs theme="race">brown</rs></rs>.</l>   
                </lg>
                </lg>
                <byline>Countée Cullen</byline>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
